e power to control your dice rolls...)</p>\n\n<p>When a player rolls all Chupacabras, he becomes &quot;Chupacabra Loco&quot; and can capture all of one type of another animal from a player.</p>\n\n","wiki":"<p><strong>Microbadge</strong><br />\n<a href=\"/microbadge/42555\"><img alt='Microbadge: Chupacabra: Survive the Night fan' onmouseover=\"return overlib('Chupacabra: Survive the Night fan', WRAP );\" onmouseout=\"return nd();\" title=''class='mbimg'loading=\"lazy\"src=\"https://cf.geekdo-static.com/mbs/mb_42555_0.png\"></a> - Chupacabra: Survive the Night fan</p>\n\n<p><strong>Components</strong> (2013 Steve Jackson Games edition)</p>\n\n<ul>\n    <li>24 custom dice</li>\n    <li>Dice cup</li>\n    <li>Rulesheet</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>2011 Haywire Group edition:<br />\nCOMPONENTS:<br />\n24 Glow-in-the-Dark Chupacabra dice (15mm 6-sided custom black plastic: 2 Goats, 1 Cow, 1 Rooster, 1 double Rooster, 1 red Chupacabra eyes). <br />\n1 Starter chip (32mm dia. acrylic disk)<br />\n1 Reference card<br />\n1 &ldquo;Classified Document&rdquo; background information<br />\nRules (4 p.).</p>\n\n","website":{"url":"http://www.sjgames.com/dice/chupacabra/","title":"Game page (English) - Steve Jackson Games"},"imageid":"1703718","images":{"thumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/9dTo4ji6fsEZj3UC3U_Aaw__small/img/qQWa8T1_hRwpelnjnzGy3Y9hlLI=/fit-in/200x150/filters:strip_icc()/pic1703718.jpg","micro":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/9dTo4ji6fsEZj3UC3U_Aaw__micro/img/L3J0x2-TTKgRbYVKAt3tTqHCKqs=/fit-in/64x64/filters:strip_icc()/pic1703718.jpg","square":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/9dTo4ji6fsEZj3UC3U_Aaw__square/img/vRsoIyFPbGQkSIPpFeUcc5Vu89A=/75x75/filters:strip_icc()/pic1703718.jpg","tallthumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/9dTo4ji6fsEZj3UC3U_Aaw__tallthumb/img/E7a-gScDBcGGsFE1MBhgWLsZtFI=/fit-in/75x125/filters:strip_icc()/pic1703718.jpg","previewthumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/9dTo4ji6fsEZj3UC3U_Aaw__previewthumb/img/2drd43xJq-pXEhpSMJJJCLcwm2Q=/fit-in/300x320/filters:strip_i